- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): Similar to cs.LG, the paper involves the use of different techniques for forecasting, which can fall under the umbrella of artificial intelligence.
- cs.SI (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the use of forecasts for electricity production, which can fall under the category of systems and control.
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper mentions the use of neural networks for forecasting, which falls under the category of neural computing.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): Similar to cs.SI, the paper discusses the use of forecasts for electricity production, which can fall under the category of systems and control.
